  "description": "Public Part III biology-and-medicine archive for the Constraint-Driven Flux Dynamics project. The release includes a seventeen-paper manuscript spine, LaTeX sources, supplementary Python scripts, generated model diagnostics, bibliography, claim-status notes, named biology laws/tests, and reproducibility instructions. The archive is open preprint material; it is not peer reviewed, not medical advice, and does not by itself establish empirical clinical validation."
